article.description: — Kayo Goncalves scored 18 points including a 3-pointer at the buzzer to give South Alabama to a 76-75 win over Southern Mississippi on Saturday.
article.headline: Goncalves' buzzer-beater lifts S. Alabama over Southern Miss
article.linkText: Goncalves' buzzer-beater lifts S. Alabama over Southern Miss
article.story: HATTIESBURG, Miss. -- — Kayo Goncalves scored 18 points including a 3-pointer at the buzzer to give South Alabama to a 76-75 win over Southern Mississippi on Saturday. Tyreke Locure added for the Jaguars (5-2). KK Curry added 16 points. Goncalves also had eight rebounds. Jaron Pierre Jr. had 25 points and 10 rebounds for the Golden Eagles (1-3). LaDavius Draine added 19 points and six assists. Artur Konontsuk had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
